Package: sms-gw
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, adduser
Description: SMS Gateway daemon with HTTP and MQTT support
 A lightweight SMS gateway daemon that accepts HTTP POST requests
 and MQTT messages to send SMS via an AT-compatible modem.
 .
 Features:
  - HTTP API for sending SMS messages
  - MQTT topic subscription for message queuing
  - Rate limiting and retry logic
  - Systemd service integration
  - Token-based authentication for HTTP
